{"tid":2176923,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★【買like工廠曝光】300手機僅連接2部電腦　即可全自動讚好及留言","createTime":"2020-08-27T11:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T11:13:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"554fdf5bb109863a7bbd8c91fa08e6088ab81450","tid":2176923,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/588248/org/124c27644902db59e49b4eaf8bc35155.jpg/huVQw-L_GqNRTVQKBfKKQm9_6BDOV1Q1knRu0ZJ0btE?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F588248%2Forg%2F124c27644902db59e49b4eaf8bc35155.jpg%2FhuVQw-L_GqNRTVQKBfKKQm9_6BDOV1Q1knRu0ZJ0btE%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=f6325bcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據片段所見，電話屏幕畫面不斷轉換，登入不同微信帳戶，對指定帖文按讚。Artem Zhdanov指，片段中手提電話為特定微信帳號推高讚好、留言數目及瀏覽量。<br />\n<br />\n兩部電腦控制數百電話<br />\n<br />\n「派like工廠」內每部電話均以線路連接電腦，最終單靠兩部電腦便可控制數百部手提電話。Artem Zhdanov又補充指，片段中的「派like工廠」已屬小型，另有大型「派like工廠」有逾萬部手提電話一同運作。<br />\n<br />\n淘寶平售讚好分享服務<br />\n<br />\n記者翻查淘寶網，不少賣家出售在facebook、Instagram、微信朋友圈及Twitter「讚好」及「轉發」服務。部份賣家標明「精準香港、台灣用戶」、「圖片讚、留言讚」；更稱「粉絲質量超高，超穩定」。這些服務價錢亦相當便宜，最平的Twitter讚好索價8元（人民幣，下同）100個，Instagram讚好則訂價15元1,000個，而讚好Facebook專頁則為10元50個。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，亦有賣家將Facebook讚好及分享的用家分門別類，中東人讚好Facebook專頁需50元500個，而「真人老外分享貼文」則訂價70元100個。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/92140/%E8%B2%B7like%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-300%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E5%83%85%E9%80%A3%E6%8E%A52%E9%83%A8%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6-%E5%8D%B3%E5%8F%AF%E5%85%A8%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E8%AE%9A%E5%A5%BD%E5%8F%8A%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80?fbclid=IwAR2yGvoddrnBEstlTLwc65qFizryqSkNaqSVauXJ2X9otRXmJNcl8et3Di8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F92140%2F%25E8%25B2%25B7like%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-300%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2583%2585%25E9%2580%25A3%25E6%258E%25A52%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6-%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25AE%259A%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%2595%2599%25E8%25A8%2580%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2yGvoddrnBEstlTLwc65qFizryqSkNaqSVauXJ2X9otRXmJNcl8et3Di8&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk0B1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=65ea5949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/92140/%E8%B2%B7like%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-300%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E5%83%85%E9%80%A3%E6%8E%A52%E9%83%A8%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6-%E5%8D%B3%E5%8F%AF%E5%85%A8%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E8%AE%9A%E5%A5%BD%E5%8F%8A%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80?fbclid=IwAR2yGvoddrnBEstlTLwc65qFizryqSkNaqSVauXJ2X9otRXmJNcl8et3Di8</a>"},{"pid":"4ea42d2ab4b49408580e968c3c7d88751b4af490","tid":2176923,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/588264/org/e984285471d59412c3ada2979473c443.png/qi-OTFRyuO3ugrmfF0JFfoVz-_mMI8FC-GyW6Phslug?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F588264%2Forg%2Fe984285471d59412c3ada2979473c443.png%2Fqi-OTFRyuO3ugrmfF0JFfoVz-_mMI8FC-GyW6Phslug%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=3f42ce61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e91bf428526ebc899b843cf644f8bac18b45059","tid":2176923,"uid":231583,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:10:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a7a586a44e35baeea8ed2e623e46e2275b68b0d","tid":2176923,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:13:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}